# Imetris Timesheets (Streamlit + Google Sheets + GitHub Actions)

Free, lightweight timesheet management with:
- Streamlit (app)
- Google Sheets (data)
- GitHub Actions (email reminders from ImetrisTimesheets@gmail.com)
- Friday week-ending, weekend entries allowed
- Admin/User roles

## Setup
1) Create Google Sheet and share with your Service Account (Editor).
2) Deploy to Streamlit → Add Secrets (service account JSON + spreadsheet_id).
3) Login as admin, submit a test timesheet, approve/reject.
4) (Optional) Add GitHub Actions secrets and enable reminders.

